{'recipes' : 'The app lets user search for recipes and sort those recipes by how close they are to a music genre. Sorting is done by counting number of adjectives that are associated with both the recipe and the music genre.\nTo search for recipes, enter ingredients and/or dish name, and press search.\nSelect music genre to sort - the closest matched recipe is in the upper left.\nClicking "show words" will display the adjectives that matched recipe to the genre.','twitter' : ['The app lets user select a headline then using a light NLP algorithm figures out which words from the headline are best suited to query twitter.\nThe search terms can be edited.\nThe tweets in the results of the query are passed through sentiment analysis tool. The per hour averages of the sentiment scores are displayed in a line graph.'}
